column33: Change​.​org: # ENOUGH is ENOUGH  # Justice for Johnny Depp
column34:
Justice for  Johnny Depp !   

If you were falsely accused of something you did not do, then there’s proof you didn’t do it and you still were treated like a bad person, wouldn’t you want Justice??

Amber Heard ruined Johnny Depp’s life as well as career. Johnny Depp has always been one of the greatest actors ever. Johnny Depp deserves his life back !

Considering that Amber Heard is a gold digger liar and an abuser. I ask YOU to help get the justice that he deserves 

Justice for Johnny Depp and all the others REAL ( DV ) victims  

Men / Woman and Children need to be protected against DV

This kind of Injustices that has been going on for far to long.
